---
import PageShell from '../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'overview', text: 'Overview', level: 2 },
  { id: 'coverage-comparison', text: 'Coverage Comparison', level: 2 },
  { id: 'pricing', text: 'Pricing', level: 2 },
  { id: 'network-and-claims', text: 'Network and Claims', level: 2 },
  { id: 'who-should-choose', text: 'Who Should Choose Which', level: 2 },
  { id: 'verdict', text: 'Our Verdict', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'BUPA Global Review', href: '/providers/bupa-global' },
  { title: 'Aetna International Review', href: '/providers/aetna-international' },
  { title: 'Best Expat Insurance', href: '/best/expat-health-insurance' },
];

const coverageColumns = [
  { key: 'feature', header: 'Feature' },
  { key: 'bupa', header: 'BUPA Global' },
  { key: 'aetna', header: 'Aetna International' },
];

const coverageRows = [
  { feature: 'Inpatient Care', bupa: true, aetna: true },
  { feature: 'Outpatient Care', bupa: true, aetna: true },
  { feature: 'Mental Health', bupa: 'Better than average', aetna: 'Moderate' },
  { feature: 'Maternity', bupa: '10-12 mo wait', aetna: '10-12 mo wait' },
  { feature: 'Dental', bupa: 'Optional', aetna: 'Optional' },
  { feature: 'Chronic Conditions', bupa: 'Strong support', aetna: 'Covered' },
  { feature: 'Telemedicine', bupa: true, aetna: true },
  { feature: 'Medical Evacuation', bupa: true, aetna: true },
  { feature: 'US Coverage', bupa: 'Add-on', aetna: 'Included (most plans)' },
];

const pricingColumns = [
  { key: 'age', header: 'Age' },
  { key: 'bupa', header: 'BUPA Global' },
  { key: 'aetna', header: 'Aetna International' },
];

const pricingRows = [
  { age: '30', bupa: '$170-260/mo', aetna: '$160-250/mo' },
  { age: '40', bupa: '$230-350/mo', aetna: '$220-340/mo' },
  { age: '50', bupa: '$300-460/mo', aetna: '$290-440/mo' },
  { age: '60', bupa: '$450-680/mo', aetna: '$420-640/mo' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="BUPA Global vs Aetna International"
  description="Compare BUPA Global and Aetna International health insurance. Two premium insurers with different strengths for expats."
  headline="BUPA Global vs Aetna International"
  subheadline="Premium tier head-to-head. UK service excellence vs US healthcare integration."
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Get Quotes from Both"
  ctaButtonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
>
  <h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>
  <p>
    BUPA Global and Aetna International are both premium-tier international health insurers. BUPA is known for exceptional customer service and mental health coverage, while Aetna offers seamless US healthcare integration.
  </p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">BUPA Global</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>UK-headquartered, service-focused</li>
        <li>Best-in-class mental health coverage</li>
        <li>Excellent customer service reputation</li>
        <li>Strong chronic condition management</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Aetna International</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>CVS Health backed (US)</li>
        <li>US coverage included by default</li>
        <li>CVS prescription integration</li>
        <li>Strong Americas network</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <CTABox
    title="Compare Premium Options"
    description="Get quotes from both premium insurers."
    buttonText="Get Free Quotes"
    buttonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <h2 id="coverage-comparison">Coverage Comparison</h2>
  <p>
    As premium insurers, both offer comprehensive coverage. The differences are in specializations—BUPA excels at mental health and service, Aetna at US integration.
  </p>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={coverageColumns} rows={coverageRows} />
  </div>

  <p><strong>Key differences:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>BUPA has notably better mental health coverage and support programs</li>
    <li>Aetna includes US coverage by default; BUPA charges extra</li>
    <li>BUPA offers superior chronic condition management programs</li>
    <li>Aetna has CVS prescription benefits for US purchases</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="pricing">Pricing</h2>
  <p>
    Pricing is similar between these premium insurers. Aetna may appear cheaper because US coverage is included.
  </p>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={pricingColumns} rows={pricingRows} />
  </div>

  <p><strong>Pricing notes:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>BUPA prices exclude US coverage; add 30-40% for US inclusion</li>
    <li>Aetna prices include US coverage</li>
    <li>BUPA may offer Medical History Disregarded options at higher premium</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="network-and-claims">Network and Claims</h2>

  <h3>Provider Networks</h3>
  <p>
    <strong>BUPA Global</strong> has extensive direct billing worldwide with particularly strong networks in Europe, Middle East, and Asia.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>Aetna International</strong> excels in the Americas with CVS Health integration providing seamless US access.
  </p>

  <h3>Customer Service</h3>
  <p>
    BUPA consistently receives higher customer service ratings. Their dedicated care teams and proactive outreach set them apart. Aetna's service is good but more transactional.
  </p>

  <h2 id="who-should-choose">Who Should Choose Which</h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Choose BUPA Global If:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>Mental health coverage is important</li>
        <li>You have chronic conditions</li>
        <li>Customer service quality is a priority</li>
        <li>You're based in Europe, Middle East, or Asia</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Choose Aetna International If:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>You need seamless US coverage</li>
        <li>You want CVS prescription benefits</li>
        <li>You're American living abroad</li>
        <li>You're based in the Americas</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="verdict">Our Verdict</h2>
  <p>
    Both are excellent premium choices. BUPA Global edges ahead for service quality and mental health coverage—important for long-term expats who want a healthcare partner, not just an insurer.
  </p>
  <p>
    Aetna International is the better choice for Americans who need integrated US coverage and prescription benefits. The CVS connection provides real value for those who use it.
  </p>

  <CTABox
    title="Ready to Decide?"
    description="Get quotes from both premium providers."
    buttonText="Compare Plans Now"
    buttonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Prices and coverage details change. Verify all information with providers before purchasing.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
